name: QR_Base_Prospect_Online_N_Importune_AeC_05
queryText:
SELECT B.CPF,
      CASE WHEN B.VALIDA_NAO_IMPORTUNE = 1 AND N5.TELEFONE IS NOT NULL OR Nao_Importune = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS Nao_Importune
FROM 	Tb_Base_Prospect_ComOTC_Online_Tratada_AeC B 
INNER JOIN TB_BASE_NAO_IMPORTUNE N5 ON ISNULL(CONCAT(DDD_05, TEL_05), '00000000000') = LTRIM(RTRIM(N5.TELEFONE))
